"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kiz1665703008492.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kiz1665703008492.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kiz1665703008492.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kiz1665703008492\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $modelname\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kiz1665703008492___modelname_274706\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the value of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Model</span> property (the suffix of the entity name) of the specified entity\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__p_d85982e1_d85983e1_d85984e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$modelname</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__p_d85985e1_d85986e1_d85987e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vReturn=$modelname(CUSTOMER)</code>\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__topic_d57167e1_d57168e1_d57169e1_d57170e1_d57171e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d837148e82\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__li_d34760e1_d34761e1_d34762e1\">Name of the model of the specified entity (in uppercase).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__li_d34763e1_d34764e1_d34765e1\">Empty string (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>), if there is\n               no current entity (that is, if the last node of the active path is not a field or\n               entity), or the current entity has no <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Model</span> value. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__topic_d57172e1_d57173e1_d57174e1_d57175e1_d57176e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d837148e103\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__topic_d57177e1_d57178e1_d57179e1_d57180e1_d57181e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d837148e113\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__p_d86000e1_d86001e1_d86002e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$modelname</span> function is useful\n            when you are writing global ProcScript functions, because it allows you to generalize\n            your code. It is also useful to examine this function when you are using the Debugger to\n            step through ProcScript statements. You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$modelname</span> from\n            everywhere within the component.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__section_pf2_ywb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d837148e128\">Example: Returning the Fully Qualified Name of the Current Field</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following ProcScript example returns the full qualified name of\n               the current field:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kiz1665703008492__pre_udb_cxb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">function FullQualifiedFieldName\n returns string\n return $concat(\"$fieldname\",\".\",$entname,\".\",$modelname)\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614128\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614128\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$modelname Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $modelname Return the value of the Model property (the suffix of the entity name) of the specified entity $modelname { ( EntityName ) } Example: vReturn=$modelname(CUSTOMER) Return Values Name of the model of the specified entity (in uppercase). Empty string ( \"\" ), if there is no current entity (that is, if the last node of the active path is not a field or entity), or the current entity has no Model value. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $modelname function is useful when you are writing global ProcScript functions, because it allows you to generalize your code. It is also useful to examine this function when you are using the Debugger to step through ProcScript statements. You can use $modelname from everywhere within the component. Example: Returning the Fully Qualified Name of the Current Field The following ProcScript example returns the full qualified name of the current field: function FullQualifiedFieldName returns string return $concat(\"$fieldname\",\".\",$entname,\".\",$modelname) end Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}